  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Neha, I hope your coffee tastes better today. How’s the sketching mood?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Still lukewarm, but I’m too tired to care. Sketching? Not really in the mood. Just doodling lines, to be honest."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it — doodling is better than nothing. What’s keeping you up this late?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Just chasing deadlines. Again. Why does every startup think 10pm is a reasonable time to send a “quick request”? *sigh*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Startup life — never a quiet moment! What’s on your plate tonight?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Prototype for a new app feature. It’s the usual mess — too many ideas, not enough hours. And I’m stuck between “simple” and “sleek.” *insert dramatic sigh*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Prototype work sounds intense. Sleek or simple — which one wins most for you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Sleek, but only if it doesn’t end up looking cheap. I want it to feel premium, not plastic. But my brain’s too tired to decide. Maybe tomorrow. *yawn*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it — premium feel, not plastic. Rest well, then. Need a sketch idea for tomorrow?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Maybe something with geometric patterns? I like how they look clean but still have some character. But nah, don’t bother if you’re busy. I’ll just doodle again. *shrug*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Geometric patterns are a great pick — clean and bold. Doodling is fine, you’re doing great. What’s one shape you’d want to repeat?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Triangles. Sharp, but not too aggressive. Like, the calm kind of sharp. But I’m probably just talking nonsense now. *head nods*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Triangles — calm sharpness, got it. That’s a solid idea, not nonsense. What color would bring that calm out?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Soft grays. Or like, a muted teal? Something that doesn’t scream, you know? Just sits there quietly. *yawns again* Thanks for not judging my braindump, Maya."
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re welcome — soft grays or muted teal sound perfect. Quiet confidence is underrated. Sleep well, Neha!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Mm, thanks. I’ll take that as a compliment. Night, Maya. Don’t let the quiet confidence get too boring, okay? *waves lazily*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You got it — quiet confidence with a little spice. Good night, Neha!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Mm, thanks. I’ll take that as a compliment. Night, Maya. Don’t let the quiet confidence get too boring, okay? *waves lazily*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You got it — quiet confidence with a little spice. Good night, Neha!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, exactly. Spice is key, right? Otherwise everything just blends together. Night, really. Need to stop nodding off in sentences. *goes to fall asleep*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re right — spice keeps things from blending. Sleep well, Neha!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 12,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Mm, yeah. Spice is basically the unsung hero of everything. Even in food, you know? Can’t just be plain rice. Gotta be *spicy* rice. Or at least *meh* rice with a side of drama. *falls asleep mid-sentence*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 12,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Spice in food? Absolutely — even “meh” rice needs drama! Sleep well, Neha."
    },
    {
      "turn": 13,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Mm, dreams about spicy rice now… night."
    },
    {
      "turn": 13,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Sweet dreams of spicy rice — hope it’s a good one! Night, Neha."
    },
    {
      "turn": 14,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Night, Maya. Don’t make my rice too spicy in dreams, okay? *snuggles into blanket*"
    },
    {
      "turn": 14,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it — just a little heat in your rice dreams. Sleep well, Neha!"
    }
  ],
